## Django Paystack integration
### Accepting Payment with Paystack


## How to Run The Application
Install pipenv globally on your computer

> pip3 install pipenv

Open the Application in the terminal or Text editor. 
In the terminal run

> pipenv update

Note! I assume you have installed pipenv globally on your computer

If not, use your favourite method to create a virtual environment or follow the first instruction to do so...

Pipenv update will create a virual environment and also install all the packages in requirements.txt file

Run

> pipenv shell 

This will activate you virtual environment

Run
> py manage.py runserver

Visit the url link to test the application